{"tid":627791,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇試過令人失望 但佢忍住唔表現 仲安慰返你？","createTime":"2018-04-13T09:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T06:47:58.000Z","uid":87540,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d93f1202aa7b40e787d132fd6017ee36e926b0c2","tid":627791,"uid":87540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T09:25:27.000Z","msg":"都好多年前...<br />\n最後一年同隊友參加比賽，但嗰日發揮唔係咁好，最後輸咗 。<br />\n我自責到仆街，但隊友都冇怪我，仲一齊安慰返我，不過我知大家其實都好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰一刻嘅感受我諗我一世都忘記唔倒<br />\n<br />\n大家又有冇類似經歷？"},{"pid":"af4139001e25f903f1081a4e9500a9ffd433c9c3","tid":627791,"uid":7615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T09:55:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"613c94e6d922d0e5e4aa1eaf9248bf7e6d61a3a1","tid":627791,"uid":87540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af4139001e25f903f1081a4e9500a9ffd433c9c3","tid":627791,"uid":7615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T09:55:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T10:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff073ffeaec2a1ceac50ce31950de0a1454ae1f","tid":627791,"uid":14131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T06:47:58.000Z","msg":"互相扶持嘅好隊友<br />\n如果你問心，當日係另一個隊友失準搞到輸咗<br />\n你會唔會怪責佢？<br />\n如果唔會咁你就唔洗內疚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}